Scenario: Authorization Link Item Query
Given I have DeviceInfo resource
!-- Known Authorization Link Items
When I get Authorization Link Item with Link Type{creditauthorization} and StoreID{00031} and POSLink ID{posLinkID110}
Then I should get POSLinkInfo model with JSON format:
{"POSLinkInfo":{"LinkID":"posLinkID110","LinkName":"POS Terminal 110","RetailStoreID":"00031"},"NCRWSSResultCode":0,"NCRWSSExtendedResultCode":0}

When I get Authorization Link Item with Link Type{creditauthorization} and StoreID{00031} and POSLink ID{posLinkID115}
Then I should get POSLinkInfo model with JSON format:
{"POSLinkInfo":{"LinkID":"posLinkID115","LinkName":"POS Terminal 115","RetailStoreID":"00031"},"NCRWSSResultCode":0,"NCRWSSExtendedResultCode":0}

!-- Authorization Link Not Found
When I get Authorization Link Item with Link Type{creditauthorization} and StoreID{25031} and POSLink ID{posLinkID115}
Then the POSLinkInfo model should be null
Then the result code should be 907

!-- Empty RetailStoreID
When I get Authorization Link Item with Link Type{creditauthorization} and StoreID{} and POSLink ID{posLinkID115}
Then the POSLinkInfo model should be not null
Then the result code should be 224

!-- Empty POS Link ID
When I get Authorization Link Item with Link Type{creditauthorization} and StoreID{0031} and POSLink ID{}
Then the POSLinkInfo model should be not null
Then the result code should be 224

!-- Invalid Link Type
